{"type": "article", "id": 15233, "title": "College Pennant", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-22T06:38:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135113OkHK1loavZCLFTpr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tadidas Originals 的秋冬系列推出了以经典款型 Stan Smith 为原型的新品 College Pennant ，不过，鹅黄、西瓜红与深蓝这三种纯色已难见原本小白鞋的踪影。鞋跟处使用了撞色系，对比鲜明。左右两只后跟分别印有“Stan”和“Smith”，以纪念这个拥有无数延伸版本的经典款型。鞋身使用麂皮，<a href=\"http://www.billys-tokyo.net/shop/e/e0050/\" target=\"_blank\">目前在日本 BILLY’S 网店有售。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142509cNdkXZCa8pLYt9u0.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142509X5FPpAJW8ijornvu.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142509POH4JG1zu0B3xaVA.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142510VIhbxcJSlL1Yzg8R.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142511lisQLfFjOC63a4So.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}